his improves the best known parameterized inapproximability\nresult, which rules out approximations with a factor of $\\text{poly} (\\log k)$,\nbut requires us to assume ETH instead of $W[1] \\neq FPT$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 May 2019 02:28:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 18 May 2019 12:10:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-21"}
